.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, canasta, billiard
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. the person playing canasta is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the cat and the person playing go have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the dog and the person playing backgammon have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person playing backgammon is not the owner of the dog##6
7. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person playing go##1
9. the owner of the pony is not the person playing billiard##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | go | canasta | billiard  | backgammon |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

