2. the owner of the ferret and the person eating blueberry have the same parity positions##9
3. the person eating peas is the owner of the pony##1
4. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5
6. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |  2   |     3     |      4       |
| Job   | pumpkin | peas | blueberry | potato |
| Pet   | goat         | pony | ferret    | chinchilla   |

