2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person watching zombie movies have different parity positions##9
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | disaster | spy | superhero   | zombie   |
| Hobby   | skydiving  | puzzles   | magic-tricks | gardening |

