.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, scooter, train
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, italian, turkish
1. the person driving the train is not the turkish##6
2. the turkish is not to the right of the canadian##8
3. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
4. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person driving the boat is the colombian##1
9. the person driving the train and the canadian have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | snowmobile   | train    | scooter | boat    |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian | italian   | colombian |

