There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, sprite, fanta
1. the person eating peach and the person drinking fanta have the same parity positions##9
2. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
3. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking fanta##7
4. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person eating mango##7
5. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person eating tomato##6
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
