.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-18::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, security-guard, writer
There 4 different types of food: lemon, kale, pear, cabbage
1. the writer and the person eating lemon have the same parity positions##9
2. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the security-guard is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
4. the writer is not to the right of the freelancer##8
5. the person eating lemon is in an even position##4
6. the person eating pear and the electrician have the same parity positions##9
7. the person eating lemon and the security-guard have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | electrician | writer | freelancer | security-guard |
| Pet   | pear    | kale   | cabbage        | lemon            |

