1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker and the person who's hobby is skydiving have the same parity positions##9
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | blend    | tiparillo | montecristo | havana |
| Hobby      | puzzles | skydiving   | board-games   | baking   |

